headline: Can Deere’s Stock Rally Continue After Recent Infrastructure Investment Surge?
summary: If you are staring at Deere’s stock ticker trying to decide your next move, you’re not alone. Deere has always had its loyal followers, but recently, with the stock hovering near $471.67, plenty are wondering just how much upside is left. Year-to-date, Deere has posted a solid 12.8% gain, and it is up a remarkable 127.7% over the last five years. Sure, the past month has been a little choppy with a 4.9% dip.
